{"id":320485,"type":3,"name":"The Lost Eden（中文版）","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/45/7d/320485_tlZLk.jpg","summary":"《The Lost Eden》是由漫画家白猫sunny所作漫画《雏蜂》同名改编动画的片头曲。明快的节奏和激烈的曲风，是一首典型的“燃曲”，完美诠释了《雏蜂》的近未来战斗格局。\r\n主题曲主创人员皆为国内二次元音乐知名制作人。曲作者战场原妖精是国内知名P主，代表作《梦回还》《韶音赋》《造梦器》《Newborn》《星灭》。词作者沈病娇为众多二次元歌曲填写中文歌词。主唱呦猫隶属SUTEIMA乐队，经常出没于各大漫展的舞台。","info":"<li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/40185\">呦猫UNEKO</a></li><li><span>编曲: </span><a href=\"/person/36413\">战场原妖精</a></li><li><span>版本特性: </span>Digital</li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2015-09-23</li><li><span>播放时长: </span>3 分</li><li><span>碟片数量: </span>1</li>","eps":[{"id":0,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/0","type":0,"sort":0,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":""}],"disc":[{"title":"Disc 1","disc":[{"title":"1 The Lost Eden","href":"/ep/991739"}]}],"staff":[{"id":40185,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4b/01/40185_prsn_S8WQW.jpg","name":"呦猫UNEKO","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":36413,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d1/12/36413_prsn_3Wtff.jpg","name":"孔德珮","desc":"编曲"}],"relations":[{"id":112133,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c3/a5/112133_uDSsr.jpg","title":"雏蜂","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/112133"}]}